*Crkvu* je podigao moj pradjed. (My grandfather built the church.)
Molim se Bogu u *crkvi*. (I pray to God in the church.)
Godina dana sam proveo radjenjem u *crkvi*. (I spent a year working on the church.)
Svake nedelje idem u *crkvu*. (I go to the church every week.)
Moj otac je bio ministar u *crkvi*. (My father was a minister at the church.)
U *crkvi* su često održavane službe. (Services were often held at the church.)
Volim da izlazim i vidim *crkve*. (I love to go out and see churches.)
U *crkvi* su se slavili veliki praznici. (Great holidays were celebrated in the church.)
*Crkve* su se gradele širom sveta. (Churches were built all over the world.)